data.description: Carbn is back with its latest property in Lake Worth Beach. This charming mid-century home has been fully renovated including an updated electrical panel, new tankless hot water, new HVAC (complete system), a new roof (to be completed prior to closing), a new fence, and an extended driveway to accommodate a second vehicle or a cool new toy. Furniture is *not* included in the sales price, but almost everything is available for purchase.
